ing, compute, now memory has lead times stretching to a year and photonics components are next. Each time one constraint loosens another appears. not necessarily a bubble indicator but it does complicate the 'build it and they'll pay' thesis."}}}, "rest_id": "2056524844523561227", "source": "<a href="https://mobile.twitter.com" rel="nofollow">Twitter Web App</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "2428", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}

