text:
@grok hi can you explain why photonics, compute , memory, power, infrastructure, lasers, interconnectors are so important for AI, rockets, satellites, drones, robotics, data centers etc?

Why does it make sense to be distributed amongst all these categories as we build out the infrastructure for this new technology over the next ten years

Also explain how difficult it is to ramp up productions on this extremely skilled labor

